<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="10Jan1937"><font color="red">10 January 1937</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I have not even yet, however, asked Mr Eliot if he has an extra page 182 of the new typescript but will write to him soon &hellip; When I was in Paris Mrs Jolas told me she hoped that Mr Jolas on his return from the U.S.A. would recommend Mr Joyce for the Nobel Prize. </div>
